# Tic-Tac-Toe AI

A terminal-based Tic-Tac-Toe game written in Python.

## Features

- Player vs Player
- Easy AI (Random)
- Impossible AI (Minimax)

## Concepts Used

- Recursion
- Backtracking
- Minimax Algorithm
- Game Trees

## How to Run

```bash
python main.py
```

## What I Learned

- Recursive problem solving
- State-space search
- Backtracking
- Designing game logic separately from UI